it all looks like false bottom + mash tun cooler conversion kit. short hose goes from your false bottom to the spigot on the inside. #2 goes on #10, #9 connects #3 + #8.white tubing looks like high temp tubing for the outside of the mash tun spigot.#3 is definately for a 10 gallon rubbermaid mash tun conversion.not sure what you mean that you pump from your mashtun.
